/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eArmor:\u003c\/strong\u003e Light \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.skullsplitterdice.com\/pages\/dnd5e-armor.html\"\u003earmor\u003c\/a\u003e, medium \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.skullsplitterdice.com\/pages\/dnd5e-armor.html\"\u003earmor\u003c\/a\u003e, shields \u003cstrong\u003eWeapons:\u003c\/strong\u003e Simple \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.skullsplitterdice.com\/pages\/dnd5e-weapons.html\"\u003eweapons\u003c\/a\u003e, martial \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.skullsplitterdice.com\/pages\/dnd5e-weapons.html\"\u003eweapons\u003c\/a\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eTools:\u003c\/strong\u003e None\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSaving Throws:\u003c\/strong\u003e Strength, Constitution\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSkills:\u003c\/strong\u003e Choose two from Animal Handling, Athletics,\u003c\/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIntimidation, Nature, Perception, and Survival\u003c\/p\u003e\u003ch4 id=\"equipment\"\u003eEquipment\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou start with the following \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.skullsplitterdice.com\/pages\/dnd5e-equipment.html\"\u003eequipment\u003c\/a\u003e, in addition to the \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.skullsplitterdice.com\/pages\/dnd5e-equipment.html\"\u003eequipment\u003c\/a\u003e granted by your \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/www.skullsplitterdice.com\/pages\/dnd5e-backgrounds.html\"\u003ebackground\u003c\/a\u003e: - (\u003cem\u003ea\u003c\/em\u003e) a greataxe or (\u003cem\u003eb\u003c\/em\u003e) any martial melee weapon - (\u003cem\u003ea\u003c\/em\u003e) two handaxes or (\u003cem\u003eb\u003c\/em\u003e) any simple weapon - An explorer’s pack and four javelins\u003c\/p\u003e\u003ch4 id=\"the-barbarian\"\u003eThe Barbarian\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003ctable\u003e\n\u003cthead\u003e\u003ctr class=\"header\"\u003e\n\u003cth\u003eLevel\u003c\/th\u003e\n\u003cth\u003eProficiency Bonus\u003c\/th\u003e\n\u003cth\u003eFeatures\u003c\/th\u003e\n\u003cth\u003eRages\u003c\/th\u003e\n\u003cth\u003eRage Damage\u00